Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:45.24,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's been so long since we left our home behind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:51.49,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Drifting on the Milky Way almost every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.96,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where am I supposed to go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.04,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What're we really looking for ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:03.13,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Stumbling in the darkness, cold and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:10.01,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But a ray of hope still exists in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.52,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Rain or shine, always chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.65,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Someday, we'll fly across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:23.11,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never fearing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:27.90,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll promise that"we'll go on ! "
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:32.08,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if you're against the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.58,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never stop !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:35.33,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:40.75,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll one day rise above it all (never give up)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:44.59,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Who cares if the going's tough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:46.13,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never think !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:48.01,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Keep pushing on !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:55.10,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We can find our promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:45.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}離鄉遠行 已經歷漫長時光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:51.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}年年日日 漂泊在星河八荒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我欲去往何處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在追尋何物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:03.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}寒冷 迷茫 在黑暗中流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:10.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我心中仍存一線希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}無論風雨 始終追尋夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.65,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}總有一天 我們將橫越蒼茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:23.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}無所畏懼 展翼翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:27.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我們許下誓言 絕不退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:32.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即便逆流而上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不要停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:35.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}切莫顧盼彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:40.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}終有一日 我們將迎來風雨後的輝煌（絕不退讓）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:44.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}道阻且長又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:46.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}何必猶疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:48.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只管開拓出前進的方向
